#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.73:0.2"
msgid "8. Yamakavagga "
msgstr "8. Pairs "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 73. Paṭhamamaraṇassatisutta → paṭhamamaraṇasatisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.73:0.3"
msgid "73. Paṭhamamaraṇassatisutta "
msgstr "73. Mindfulness of Death (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.317, sc1
#. VAR: nātike → nādike (bj, s1-3) | nāṭike (pts1)
msgctxt "an8.73:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā nātike viharati giñjakāvasathe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Nādika in the brick house. "

msgctxt "an8.73:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "an8.73:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.73:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an8.73:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.73:1.6"
msgid "“maraṇassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when mindfulness of death is developed and cultivated it’s very fruitful and beneficial. It culminates in the deathless and ends with the deathless. "

#. VAR: maraṇassatin”ti → maraṇasatinti (bj)
msgctxt "an8.73:1.7"
msgid "Bhāvetha no tumhe, bhikkhave, maraṇassatin”ti. "
msgstr "But do you develop mindfulness of death?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an8.73:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, one of the mendicants said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "an8.73:2.2"
msgid "“ahaṃ kho, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, I develop mindfulness of death.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.73:2.3"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, bhāvesi maraṇassatin”ti? "
msgstr "“But mendicant, how do you develop it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.73:2.4"
msgid "“Idha mayhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "“In this case, sir, I think: "

#. VAR: bahu → bahuṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.73:2.5"
msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ rattindivaṃ jīveyyaṃ, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Oh, if I’d only live for another day and night, I’d focus on the Buddha’s instructions and I could really achieve a lot.’ "

msgctxt "an8.73:2.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti. (1) "
msgstr "That’s how I develop mindfulness of death.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
