msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ assasitvā vā passasāmi, passasitvā vā assasāmi, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Oh, if I’d only live as long as it takes to breathe out after breathing in, or to breathe in after breathing out, I’d focus on the Buddha’s instructions and I could really achieve a lot.’ "

msgctxt "an8.73:9.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti. (8) "
msgstr "That’s how I develop mindfulness of death.” "

